<section class="wide-section">
    <div class="section-content section-content-center">
        <h1>About Tayles</h1>
        <p class="lead">Tayles is a lightweight RPG campaign manager built to help Game Masters design worlds, manage player teams and reveal secrets to players in a controlled way.</p>
        <p>We focus on fast creation, clear organization and flexible permissions so GMs can concentrate on storytelling.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="section-content">
        <h2>Core features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Create and manage Worlds and Nodes (places, characters, events, objects)</li>
            <li>Attach secrets to nodes and reveal them to specific players or teams</li>
            <li>Player teams and character nodes for collaborative play</li>
            <li>Simple permissions and world membership</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

